#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Pāṇasutta "
msgstr "11. Living Creatures "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.78, sc1
msgctxt "sn46.11:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci pāṇā cattāro iriyāpathe kappenti—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, living creatures engage in the four postures: "

msgctxt "sn46.11:1.2"
msgid "kālena gamanaṃ, kālena ṭhānaṃ, kālena nisajjaṃ, kālena seyyaṃ, sabbe te pathaviṃ nissāya pathaviyaṃ patiṭṭhāya evamete cattāro iriyāpathe kappenti; "
msgstr "sometimes walking, sometimes standing, sometimes sitting, sometimes lying down. They do so depending on the earth and grounded on the earth. "

msgctxt "sn46.11:1.3"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti, satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkaroti. "
msgstr "In the same way, a mendicant develops and cultivates the seven awakening factors depending on and grounded on ethics. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.11:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkaroti? "
msgstr "And how does a mendicant develop the seven awakening factors depending on and grounded on ethics? "

msgctxt "sn46.11:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

msgctxt "sn46.11:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlaṃ nissāya sīle patiṭṭhāya satta bojjhaṅge bhāveti, satta bojjhaṅge bahulīkarotī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant develops and cultivates the seven awakening factors depending on and grounded on ethics.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.11:2.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

